Test Item: {{test_item_desc}}
Problem Description: {{problem_desc}}

Troubleshooting Suggestions:
I. Test Purpose
{{test_purpose}}

II. Failure Analysis
1. Microphone Sensitivity Abnormality
{{level_spec_fails}}
   Possible causes: Excessive microphone gain, environmental noise interference, or microphone hardware failure

2. Sampling Status Abnormality
{{status_fails}}
   Possible causes: Unstable microphone connection, sampling rate mismatch

3. Comprehensive Judgment
{{comprehensive_analysis}}

III. Recommendations
