测试项：{{test_item_desc}} 问题描述：{{problem_desc}}
排查建议： 一、测试目的 {{test_purpose}}
二、失败原因分析 1. 频率响应异常 {{level_spec_fails}} 可能原因：麦克风频响曲线偏移、测试频段内存在干扰信号或滤波电路异常
2. FFT算法处理异常 {{status_fails}} 可能原因：算法参数配置错误、采样率不匹配（采样率:44100）或计算资源不足
3. 声学耦合异常 {{comprehensive_analysis}} 可能原因：麦克风与扬声器位置不当、声学环境反射干扰或扬声器频响异常
三、改进建议 1. 校准MIC1在4-16kHz频段的频率响应曲线 2. 检查并优化FFT算法参数设置，确保与44100采样率匹配 3. 调整麦克风与SPKR1的相对位置，减少声学干扰 4. 检查测试环境，增加声学隔离措施 5. 验证FFT算法实现，必要时进行算法优化或更新


Test Item: {{test_item_desc}}
Problem Description: {{problem_desc}}

Troubleshooting Suggestions:
I. Test Purpose
{{test_purpose}}

II. Failure Analysis
1. Frequency Response Abnormality
{{level_spec_fails}}
   Possible causes: Microphone frequency response curve deviation, interference signals in test frequency band, or abnormal filter circuit

2. FFT Algorithm Processing Anomaly
{{status_fails}}
   Possible causes: Incorrect algorithm parameter configuration, sampling rate mismatch (sampling rate:44100), or insufficient computing resources

3. Acoustic Coupling Anomaly
{{comprehensive_analysis}}

III. Recommendations
1. Calibrate the frequency response curve of MIC1 in 4-16kHz band
2. Check and optimize FFT algorithm parameter settings to ensure matching with 44100 sampling rate
3. Adjust the relative position of microphone and SPKR1 to reduce acoustic interference
4. Inspect the test environment and add acoustic isolation measures
5. Verify FFT algorithm implementation and optimize or update the algorithm if necessary

