测试项：{{test_item_desc}} 问题描述：{{problem_desc}}
排查建议： 一、测试目的 {{test_purpose}}
二、失败原因分析 1. 灵敏度响应异常 {{level_spec_fails}} 可能原因：EAR传感器灵敏度漂移、测试频段内信号衰减异常或增益调节不当
2. 音频信号同步异常 {{status_fails}} 可能原因：时钟源不同步、数据传输延迟超标或MIC1与EAR采样相位偏差
3. 频率响应特性异常 {{comprehensive_analysis}} 可能原因：频率响应曲线非线性失真、测试频段内稳定性指标不达标或滤波特性异常
三、改进建议 1. 重新校准EAR在140Hz至7100Hz频段的灵敏度参数 2. 优化MIC1与EAR的同步机制，确保时钟和采样相位一致 3. 调整频率响应曲线，提升线性度和稳定性指标 4. 验证并修正与KANSA产品的接口协议和通信参数 5. 升级相关固件版本，确保系统兼容性 6. 优化测试环境，减少外部干扰对灵敏度和同步性能的影响

Test Item: {{test_item_desc}} Problem Description: {{problem_desc}}
Troubleshooting Suggestions: I. Test Purpose {{test_purpose}}
II. Failure Analysis 1. Sensitivity Response Abnormality {{level_spec_fails}} Possible causes: EAR sensor sensitivity drift, abnormal signal attenuation in test frequency band, or improper gain adjustment
2. Audio Signal Synchronization Anomaly {{status_fails}} Possible causes: Clock source asynchrony, excessive data transmission delay, or sampling phase deviation between MIC1 and EAR
3. Frequency Response Characteristic Anomaly {{comprehensive_analysis}} Possible causes: Non-linear distortion of frequency response curve, unstable indicators in test frequency band, or abnormal filtering characteristics
III. Recommendations 1. Recalibrate EAR sensitivity parameters in 140Hz to 7100Hz frequency band 2. Optimize synchronization mechanism between MIC1 and EAR to ensure consistent clock and sampling phase 3. Adjust frequency response curve to improve linearity and stability indicators 4. Verify and correct interface protocols and communication parameters with KANSA products 5. Upgrade relevant firmware versions to ensure system compatibility 6. Optimize test environment to reduce external interference on sensitivity and synchronization performance

